-- Description
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- This entity implements the cl_fix_add function as entity. Includes pipeline stages
-- and allows usage from Verilog.
--
-- Documentation:
-- https://github.com/open-logic/open-logic/blob/main/doc/fix/olo_fix_add.md
--
